/span></div><div>(originally posted by @CalzoneBoy900 on 2023-06-23 07:12:26)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/GYIgiYz</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ThisTimeLastYear]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>How I met your mother.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DCvKQ5o</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dLqWB8F.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Cameraman saves the day.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/DCvKQ5o</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WeirdAlisMySpiritUserName]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Bi/Pan Mini-Dump</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/y0ywSts</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/d8UVQ4A.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>As promised, here's the bisexual mini-dump I planned to do. Generally bi and pan mean the same thing, right? I'd say just use whichever one you feel more comfortable with, or whichever flag color scheme you like more. I'm no expert on the subject though, if someone would like to correct me. I identify with both a little, but a more specific label fits me better.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kjyrRPH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I do love this color scheme, and somehow it got even better.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RAnT39R.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/DGoJe36.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I love this one so much. Leanbeefpatty and F1nn5ter for those who aren't aware. It was someone posting this image here on Imgur that got me to look into F1nn and following him taught me so much about myself and it's been life changing honestly. That, and his adorable chaotic energy is a lot of fun anyway. His Coming Out video (https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=3reFDwM0yIA) where he comes out as Genderfluid (prefers he/him) and being on HRT, and being bisexual helped me so much. Inspired to come out of the closet a little more tonight, (am trans) but maybe not about the bisexuality, which if we get specific for me is probably fin(n)sexuality, lol.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7RYrOtG.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I adore them so much. There's a "bisexual sitting meme" where bisexuals can't sit normally and I felt it so much, lol.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4R5o8f5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Maybe I need this.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kcYg5qg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I want this so much. "Equal opportunity sexiness" I believe?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CvBWAjC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I think someone made this because of the popularity of the reaction GIF. Surely there's another girl in Road to El Dorado for Chel to kiss though...?</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/tBxSPYP.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/CXlCLj1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I wonder if someone actually came out this way.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/pHLdFgW.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zxlwbhU.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Xcp2ZzR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>This was brought to my attention in one of my "Roommates Mini-Dumps", so ridiculously cute.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/L3yKbR0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/cR9rLfC.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/y0ywSts</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MermaidNinja]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>The Naked Gun 1988 - &quot;Maybe this will help ...&quot; Bribe Scene - Enhanced GIF DL</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/OkXmNRo</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Bk3imoP.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/OkXmNRo</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DietLoki]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Crossing…</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/s4PsbxB</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Z0igc25.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/s4PsbxB</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[tractorist]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Naturally cubed Pyrite crystals</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/tNv5gm6</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GOZEUyy.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tNv5gm6</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[AbithiOtherHalf]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Marisa Tomei senior yearbook photo, 1982</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/IbZElG4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GVdULyx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/IbZElG4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[HotPinkk]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Russian family values. Russia doesn’t treat its soldiers as humans.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/MsO4PvO</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="http