 The results were sobering.

Underpinning a bewildering number of moving parts is the likelihood that space agencies are not ready to implement the operations needed to find out more about the threat and mitigate it, even with more than a decade to prepare.

"The process for making decisions about space missions in an asteroid threat scenario remains unclear. The process has not been adequately defined in the US or internationally"
https://www.theregister.com/2024/06/21/nasa_asteroid_defence/
In the scenario... there is Washington DC as a good target

Since we are in the 21st century, and with everything going on in the world, I wouldn't be surprised if there wasn't really asteroids out there that are growing tired of just flying about in space, and decided to go out with a bang, it's happened before, when will it happen again?</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/VSU96md</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[OregonComputerGuy]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Bro is a legend</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/CGdcIuY</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/UvIp5qH.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/CGdcIuY</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Seunaike]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Behind the Scenes...</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/YynQPvu</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/oiawUsR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Watch out... doing more absurdist content again for Imgur's upcoming Upvote Everything Day...</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/YynQPvu</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Alsoashley]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>A few messages I saved over the years</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Fhf52he</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/KboJzB3.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/K6CudOG.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/eJ3aDnF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/21NA6ZC.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/SK6r8TJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/8LRed5c.jpg